cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.DB 

The paper is about neural models for information retrieval, specifically for product search. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IR (Information Retrieval). The paper also discusses the use of graph embedding techniques, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves natural language processing (cs.CL) as it deals with semantic matching. The use of external heterogeneous information also suggests the category of information systems (cs.SI) and databases (cs.DB).
